[{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/rclone/rclone/issues/comments/535952745","html_url":"https://github.com/rclone/rclone/issues/3573#issuecomment-535952745","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/rclone/rclone/issues/3573","id":535952745,"node_id":"MDEyOklzc3VlQ29tbWVudDUzNTk1Mjc0NQ==","user":{"login":"ncw","id":536803,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjUzNjgwMw==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/536803?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw","html_url":"https://github.com/ncw","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2019-09-27T14:03:01Z","updated_at":"2019-09-27T14:03:01Z","body":"> The problem / bug is that http://127.0.0.1:53682/auth is not unique - any user on a shared platform can connect\r\n\r\nUnfortunately that URL needs to be configured at box as the redirection URL so it isn't possible to change it on the fly.\r\n\r\nI managed to replicate this.\r\n\r\nI notice that when you start the second rclone and get to the webserver prompt you get this and rclone stops\r\n\r\n```\r\nUse auto config?\r\n * Say Y if not sure\r\n * Say N if you are working on a remote or headless machine\r\ny) Yes\r\nn) No\r\ny/n> y\r\n2019/09/27 13:52:00 Failed to start auth webserver: listen tcp 127.0.0.1:53682: bind: address already in use\r\n```\r\n\r\nHowever rclone has already opened the browser window at that point and popped it to the front.\r\n\r\nSo I propose two fixes\r\n\r\n1. open the browser window after we have successfully started the oauth server\r\n    - this would have fixed the problem on its own\r\n2. check the unique state in the auth redirect is correct\r\n    - this would also have fixed the problem on its own\r\n\r\nCan you have a go with this fix and see if it fixes it for you?\r\n\r\nhttps://beta.rclone.org/branch/v1.49.3-101-gda77b2d0-fix-3573-auth-beta/ (uploaded in 15-30 mins)\r\n\r\n","author_association":"MEMBER","reactions":{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/rclone/rclone/issues/comments/535952745/reactions","total_count":0,"+1":0,"-1":0,"laugh":0,"hooray":0,"confused":0,"heart":0,"rocket":0,"eyes":0},"performed_via_github_app":null,"event":"commented","actor":{"login":"ncw","id":536803,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjUzNjgwMw==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/536803?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw","html_url":"https://github.com/ncw","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false}},{"id":2668762871,"node_id":"MDEyOkxhYmVsZWRFdmVudDI2Njg3NjI4NzE=","url":"https://api.github.com/repos/rclone/rclone/issues/events/2668762871","actor":{"login":"ncw","id":536803,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjUzNjgwMw==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/536803?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/ncw","html_url":"https://gi